milestones.description: Aminul Islam and Akram Khan's 72-run partnership is BAN's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 41 between Shaheedur Rahman and Rafiqul Alam
Khaled Mashud has broken the record for most dismissals (3) in ODIs for BAN, going past Hafizur Rahman's 2
